meanings.type: Noun, Noun, used as a suffix
meanings.meaning: 1. report; notification; registration
届け 【とどけ】
1. to deliver; to forward; to send 家に届けていただけますか。Can you deliver it to my house?
2. to report; to notify; to file notice (to the authorities); to give notice; to register 私は車が盗まれたことを警察に届けた。I reported the theft of my car to the police.
屆ける 【とどける】
屆ける: Out-dated kanji or kanji usage.

I reported the theft of my car to the police.

meanings.type: Godan verb with 'ku' ending, Intransitive verb
